# Runtime state for the mesh-control container's shared bind mount.
# Holds the Noise long-term static key + the self-signed TLS cert
# minted at first :443 bind. Regenerated automatically by
# `run-interop.sh`; safe to wipe between runs.
state/

# Wall 6 (2026-05-19) — derper-1 sidecar's TLS material. Minted by
# `run-interop.sh` at first run; regenerated on demand if absent.
# Same lifecycle as `state/` — wipe freely between runs.
derp-certs/
